            "id": "camera_cooler_off",
            "name": "Cooler/Fan Off",
            "description": "Switch the TEC cooler (and fan) off via CCD_COOLER.COOLER_OFF. Warm the sensor with a ramp beforehand to avoid thermal shock.",
